# Monorepo Structure

This project is a monorepo with the following main directories:

-   `[common/](mdc:)`: A shared library used by both the frontend and backend.
-   `[backend/](mdc:)`: Contains the backend application.
-   `[frontend/](mdc:)`: Contains the frontend application.
